{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">First released on NES, the hit cyberpunk action adventure game is now on Steam!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is not simply the original NES game wrapped in a self contained emulator like so many other NES homebrews. This game has been completely reprogrammed from the ground up! This can easily be discerned by the new dialog engine and lighting effects. <strong>Plus, the game's entire chiptune soundtrack has been re-recorded with modern rock instruments to give you the full ability to switch between modern and classic music on the fly!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a desperate attempt to stop crucial information from being leaked, an unknown source has deployed a virus that corrupts anyone who jacks into cyberspace. The virus was designed to render all data Couriers inoperable. However, there was an anomaly...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u200bHelp Conrad free the city from the control of Ankh Industries in this exciting cyberpunk adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore, pickpocket, shoot, and hack your way through many areas in order to upgrade your skills and fulfill your destiny.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hack the planet!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326000/60fcbd54176b78994bcf531568834df960d39b16.jpg"},{"name":"Upgrades are costly, eh?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326000/41e6241f70609feefeca418b5db9cf40364c7d57.jpg"},{"name":"King for a day.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326000/8d20a9f9173dfb67a326ac865e155f20f985eefa.jpg"},{"name":"Services not rendered.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2326000/8089e21d1169e404c41aad3f87e251d4d23ecc0a.jpg"},{"name":"Say hello to your lit